<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77957090-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s430h–5"><num value="430h–5">§ 430h–5.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated such sums, but not more than $3,850,000, as are required for acquisition of lands and interests in lands and for construction and relocation of roads pursuant to sections 430h–3 to 430h–5 of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77957091-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/88/37/s3">Pub. L. 88–37, § 3</ref>, <date date="1963-06-04">June 4, 1963</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/77/56">77 Stat. 56</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/94/578/tII/s201/8">Pub. L. 94–578, title II, § 201(8)</ref>, <date date="1976-10-21">Oct. 21, 1976</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/90/2733">90 Stat. 2733</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id77957092-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id77957093-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id77957094-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1976—<ref href="/us/pl/94/578">Pub. L. 94–578</ref> substituted “$3,850,000” for “$2,050,000”.</p>
</note>
